title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 8 2022
description:
California primary results foretell a huge red wave in November. Biden Commerce secretary: Nothing can be done to lower gas prices. Inez Stepman of the Independent Women's Forum and its High Noon podcast joins Clay and Buck to discuss Biden's jaw-dropping plans to redefine sex and gender. C&B cover some of the crazy viral videos out there.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
